Brownfield land

View the data

The brownfield land data on this page has been collected and processed by the Digital Land pipeline.

URL of the register:
https://datahub.bradford.gov.uk/opendata/brownfield_register/Brownfield%20Register%202019.csv
See documentation page
Published 22 December 2019
From:
City of Bradford Metropolitan District Council

How we've processed this data

The Digital Land pipeline collects the data and fixes common errors that do not align with the data standard.

Find out more about our pipeline process.

Related content

  • Validation result
  • Preprocessed resource file

About the data

This register has reported a total of 211 brownfield sites.

0 of these have an end date and are no longer considered brownfield land.

Excluding sites with an end date, there are 166.10 hectares of land.

This land has the potential to provide between 6743 and 8034 dwellings.

0 of these sites have permission in principle.

1 organisations are referenced in this file.

Site locations

All 211 sites plotted.

Records

There are 211 records after processing this brownfield register.
